data.description: Stop by and view this amazing Edward Homes resale with four bedrooms (2 masters) and three full baths. When you first enter through the front door, there is a bedroom perfect for guest or an office space. As you walk further in, you walk into the open living room/kitchen concept with a 3 panel sliding glass door that is customized with UV control window tint perfect for those hot summers. The kitchen has a large island and an added on desk area. This home is prewired with surround sound. The primary bedroom is opened by french doors. Each bedroom has walk-in closets with built in shelving. The garage has built in storage as well. You also have a bonus shed in the backyard. The covered patio has a full kitchen, outdoor lighting, and fire-pit sitting area contributing to the appeasing esthetic ensuring this home is great for entertaining guest. If you have dogs, this property has a built in area for your dogs to potty, ensuring the turf is taken cared of. Schedule your appointment before it's gone.
